# Tilmelding — Agent Rules

## Org conventions
Read `../nathejk/conventions/rules.md` for org-wide conventions before proceeding.
Everything in that file applies here unless explicitly overridden below.

---

## This repo

**Purpose:** Nathejk tilmelding, user facing frontend with dedicated api (backend for frontend style)
**Group:** Core

### Services

| Service | Technology | Dev target | Local URL |
|---|---|---|---|
| frontend | Vue 3 (TS) | `node-dev` | `https://<name>.localhost` |
| bff | Go | `go-dev` | internal only |

### Key files
- `Dockerfile` — multistage build (targets: `node-dev`, `go-dev`, `prod`)
- `docker-compose.yml` — dev environment
- `tasks/TASKS.md` — task board conventions

---

## Task board
Tasks are in `tasks/`. Read `tasks/TASKS.md` before touching any task.

---

## Repo-specific conventions

- All endpoints must have OpenAPI annotations
